<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You for Contacting React Fast Training</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0EA5E9 0%, #10B981 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 200px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #0EA5E9;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #E0F2FE;
            border-left: 4px solid #0EA5E9;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #10B981;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #059669;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .social-links a {
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #0EA5E9;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Thank You for Contacting Us!</h1>
        <p>Act Fast | Save Lives</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <div class="greeting">
            Hi {{firstName}},
        </div>
        
        <p>Thank you for reaching out to React Fast Training. We've received your message regarding "<strong>{{subject}}</strong>" and we appreciate your interest in our first aid training courses.</p>
        
        <div class="info-box">
            <strong>What happens next?</strong><br>
            One of our team members will review your message and get back to you within 24-48 hours (Monday to Friday). We aim to respond as quickly as possible to all enquiries.
        </div>
        
        <p>In the meantime, you might find these resources helpful:</p>
        
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Course Information:</strong> Learn more about our <a href="https://www.reactfasttraining.co.uk/courses">first aid courses</a></li>
            <li><strong>Training Locations:</strong> Find out about our <a href="https://www.reactfasttraining.co.uk/venue">training venues</a> across Yorkshire</li>
            <li><strong>About Us:</strong> Discover more about <a href="https://www.reactfasttraining.co.uk/about">our instructors and mission</a></li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>If your enquiry is urgent, please don't hesitate to call us directly on <strong>07447 485644</strong> during our office hours:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Monday - Friday: 8:00 AM - 6:00 PM</li>
            <li>Saturday: 9:00 AM - 4:00 PM</li>
        </ul>
        
        <center>
            <a href="https://www.reactfasttraining.co.uk/courses" class="button">Browse Our Courses</a>
        </center>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p><strong>React Fast Training</strong><br>
        Professional First Aid Training Across Yorkshire<br>
        Leeds | Sheffield | Bradford</p>
        
        <div class="social-links">
            <a href="#">Facebook</a> |
            <a href="#">LinkedIn</a> |
            <a href="#">Twitter</a>
        </div>
        
        <p style="font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px;">
            This email was sent because you submitted a contact form on our website.<br>
            If you did not submit this form, please ignore this email.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>